\id PHM - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014) 
\h Pai 
\toc3 Pai 
\toc1 Polote Leta Pailimonitamo Ododiyaêž‰ 
\toc2 Pailimoni 
\mt2 POLOTE LETA  
\mt1 PAILIMONITAMO  
\mt2 ODODIYAêž‰  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Na baêž‰ Polotela, nale Yaêž‰su Kelisoko mabumaêž‰ du genamalo emedenamo. Na baêž‰gala a hibimaêž‰ midipino ekawi Timotiko, ale baêž‰moe leta amaêž‰ Pailimonitamo poememaêž‰. Hibila, amaêž‰ baêž‰ aeno hidonomo lumagila baêž‰gala amaêž‰le ago Godokono oko bowatinata.  
\v 2 Baêž‰bene laêž‰ sose tawakalubi puyaêž‰te Pailimonikono genamalo daêž‰kapiyuiminakoma, baêž‰gala a hibimaêž‰ midipino naniko Aêž‰piyako, baêž‰gala Saitanatamo alaholo komo ago kapimilo dododina baêž‰be dubu Akipasiko, ale laêž‰ hiliyonomatamo atumu baêž‰moe leta bepoememaêž‰.   
\p
\v 3 Wadiyala aeno Nabiwi Godoko baêž‰gala Kodawa Yaêž‰su Kelisoko, ibaêž‰te ibino malemale komo baêž‰gala hete komo laêž‰tamo nikalamaêž‰menaêž‰ta.   
\s1 Polote Pailimonikono Komomaêž‰ Kalakala Tabo Dolamagiyaêž‰  
\p
\v 4 Naeno hido lumagi Pailimoni, nale dadikuminakomo baêž‰be Godotamo toetoe tabo ba olamagi amiaêž‰no komomaêž‰ nale kalakala tabo ebetamo adipatenakomo.  
\v 5 Iyo, naeno kalakala bitana mabu amaêž‰le Godokono tawakalubi hiliyonomo malemalelo demalagidolena baêž‰gala amaêž‰le Kodawa Yaêž‰suku hibimaêž‰ midi ipuwalo kodakodalo daêž‰laêž‰na, nale baêž‰bi netewa komokomo ulihonakomo.  
\v 6 Baêž‰bene nale Godoko baêž‰ma kaêž‰na toemehonakomo, amaêž‰la, ala, ale hibimaêž‰ midi ipuwalo kapiya tawakalubinomomaêž‰ dedaêž‰hanamaêž‰, baêž‰be komone ale Kelisoko ipuwalo ba emedena kebe hidohido komo Godogodone duwatenakomaêž‰, amaêž‰le baêž‰bi hiliyonomo komo hidonomamo kiyaêž‰tawamaêž‰.  
\v 7 O naeno hidonomo ekawi, baêž‰ hibila, amaêž‰ komopi malemalelo ba emalagidolena ibino tepo ipuwoeno menemene ukui daêž‰wibuilamelelamenaka, nale baêž‰be komo dulimo naeno hiyaêž‰hiyaêž‰ temeteme ipuwalo konomo gelebadi komo baêž‰gala kalakala komo baêž‰bo uwatimo!   
\s1 Polote Pailimoniko Daêž‰kiyamiyaêž‰ Ebete Onisimasiko Kalakalago Kolawemaêž‰  
\p
\v 8 Baêž‰bemaêž‰ a netewapi Kelisoko hibimaêž‰ midi ipuwalo ba emedena ebeno modobo helote na Pologodolo bitana, iyo, talona kitanahaêž‰ nale naeno ubi komo hawakalimiti amaêž‰ koamo kiyahamemaêž‰, baêž‰ma kaêž‰na amaêž‰le naeno ubi komamo dito kopapamiwatamaêž‰.  
\v 9 Huiyatiya nale amaêž‰ malemalelo demalagidolonama, baêž‰bemaêž‰ amaêž‰le naeno ubi komo ododimaêž‰ nale amaêž‰ aêž‰kakiyahamaêž‰mata, ao, na huiyatiya amaêž‰ tataba gabodo toemehomata. Amaêž‰ numaêž‰, na baêž‰ Polotela, na kadelemaêž‰ ba edaêž‰na Yaêž‰su Kelisoko mabumaêž‰ du genamalo emedenamo, baêž‰bemaêž‰ amiaêž‰no malemale natamo hibilo ditana, wadiyala baêž‰be komo hawakalimimaêž‰ amaêž‰ baêž‰moe naeno toetoe tabo komamo naêž‰papamiwatuyaêž‰.   
\p
\v 10 Baêž‰bemaêž‰ mabulubi, nale Onisimasiko\f * \fr 1.10 \ft Baêž‰moe Onisimasikono mahiloeno ipuwa nitana â€˜Hidohido Komo Ododilidawala.â€™ Ebete dopamo Pailimonikono huiyahaêž‰ okodawamaêž‰ edaêž‰nami, huiyatiya ebete Pailimonitamo daêž‰maubuyaêž‰, baêž‰ba tetelo ebete pilo komo ododiti ebegodone Loma ko habamo baêž‰ dito alahuliyaêž‰. Ebete baêž‰bolo ba nemede eta hegelalo Polokobaêž‰ daêž‰naluguyaêž‰ ebegodone Yaêž‰sukunu Hido Tabo uliti hibimaêž‰ mididawamaêž‰ baêž‰bo ediyaêž‰.\f* mabumaêž‰ amaêž‰ betoemehomata, mabu nale baêž‰moe du genamalo ba emedena ebete hibimaêž‰ midi ipuwalo naeno eta gudumaêž‰ edi.  
\v 11 Dopamo ebete amiaêž‰no genamalo ba emedena, diyala, ebete komo tetelo ebeno oko owati ipuwalo hidohido komo amaêž‰tamo daêž‰ kododilinakuihaêž‰. Kaêž‰lo huiyatiya ebete uli lumagimaêž‰ edaêž‰na, baêž‰bemaêž‰ na iyaêž‰tawala baêž‰ma tetene tupuimiti ebete amaêž‰tamo baêž‰gala natamo hidohido komo kapiya hibilo bododilinakomene.   
\p
\v 12 Baêž‰bemaêž‰ numaêž‰, nale naeno uli gudu amaêž‰tamo poememo. Naeno tepo ipuwoeno malemale komote ebetamo ditana bada konomolaêž‰kaêž‰,  
\v 13 baêž‰bemaêž‰ na ubi baêž‰ma kaêž‰na ihatimo, Yaêž‰sukunu Hido Tabo mabumaêž‰ Onisimasiti nago baêž‰moe du genamalo ba emedena natamo hido owalubi kihatenamaêž‰. Baêž‰ hibila, amaêž‰ muhululu ba emedena amaêž‰ modobohaêž‰ owalubi natamo ihate, baêž‰bemaêž‰ kubahaêž‰ amiaêž‰no okodawate amiaêž‰no haba pelawete na tamelo ba luta naeno modobohaêž‰ komokomo kododilimaêž‰ne.  
\v 14 Huiyatiya nale ukui baêž‰ba kaêž‰na ba ihatita ebe amaêž‰tamo poememaêž‰ kamawaditahaêž‰, mabu na ubihinola amaêž‰le modobo tabo goeheno ebete na dito owalubinina. Baêž‰bemaêž‰ amaêž‰la, nala, ale baêž‰moe guduino komomaêž‰ ukui kapiyamaêž‰ edaêž‰heno, nale ebe kodakodalo atilaêž‰na modobohaêž‰.   
\p
\v 15 Diyala, Godote Onisimasikono komomaêž‰ ubi baêž‰ma kaêž‰na kudaêž‰ ihati, ebete amaêž‰godone alahulaêž‰te tete nanekele amaêž‰godolo emedeheno eta habalo konemedaêž‰tepamaêž‰, huiyatiya kalakala konomola, baêž‰ma tetelo ebete amaêž‰tamo gala daêž‰kapemene ebete amaêž‰godolo tete gaêž‰gaêž‰nomolo bemedenamene, mabu hibila, baêž‰ma tetelo laêž‰ netewapaêž‰te hibimaêž‰ midi ipuwalo baêž‰ kapiya badininipalamaêž‰ edaêž‰namata.  
\v 16 Baêž‰bemaêž‰ baêž‰ma tetelo amaêž‰le ebe amiaêž‰no huiyahaêž‰ okodawamaêž‰ daêž‰goena, wadiyala amaêž‰ atu tetelo ebe amiaêž‰no hibimaêž‰ mididawa ekawi etamaêž‰ ba kaêž‰mina ebe malemalelo nemalagidolona. Hibila, Onisimasiko mabumaêž‰ naeno kalakalate konomomaêž‰ edaêž‰na, huiyatiya amaêž‰le ebe gala daêž‰kumiminaêž‰, baêž‰ba tetelo amiaêž‰no kalakala komote nagodolo ditana baêž‰be kalakala hibilo kogogolomaêž‰ne, mabu ebe baêž‰ amiaêž‰no hido okodawala baêž‰gala ebe Kodawa Yaêž‰suku ipuwalo amiaêž‰no ekawimaêž‰ edaêž‰na.   
\p
\v 17 Baêž‰bemaêž‰ amaêž‰le na Kelisoko ipuwalo amiaêž‰no hido mabulubimaêž‰ daêž‰kaêž‰namina, wadiyala amaêž‰le Onisimasiko konomo kalakalago naêž‰lawiyaêž‰, nale amaêž‰tamo daêž‰pemo baêž‰ba tetelo amaêž‰le na keba kaêž‰na naêž‰kaêž‰laweneomenaêž‰ baêž‰ba kaêž‰na.\f * \fr 1.17 \ft Poloko tetelo Loma Gabomanino tutumu tabote baêž‰ma kaêž‰na itanami, kebe huiyahaêž‰ okodawate ebeno oko namutudawagodone dalahulaêž‰mene, baêž‰be dubuti ebe gala daêž‰kumimini, ebeno kuba ododi mabumaêž‰ talona puliyala ebete ebe anakapumimaêž‰. Baêž‰bemaêž‰ Polote baêž‰be komo ba emalagidolo Pailimoniko naêž‰kiyamiyaêž‰, ebete Onisimasikono kuba egebolemete ebe kalakalago naêž‰lawaêž‰mene, heloagohaêž‰.\f*  
\v 18 Baêž‰gala ebete alahulaêž‰heno, diyala, dopamo ebete eta kuba amaêž‰tamo kudaêž‰ ododi, baêž‰ma kaêž‰na ebete pilo komo dododi, wadiyala amaêž‰ huiyatiya baêž‰be kuba naeno kubamaêž‰ naêž‰midiyaêž‰, baêž‰bemaêž‰ hibila, baêž‰be komo galane na haêž‰kiya kopetuputupuimimaêž‰nemo.  
\v 19 Amaêž‰ numaêž‰, eta lumagiti na mabumaêž‰ baêž‰moe letoeno tabo komokomo ba miyaêž‰teho, huiyatiya na Polote naeno hibi komo hawakalimimaêž‰ na haêž‰kiya naeno kokotamo baêž‰moe kapiya tabo bimiyaêž‰temo, nale Onisimasikono kuba ododi mabumaêž‰ amaêž‰tamo hibilo kopehuiyamaêž‰nemo. Huiyatiya amaêž‰le na baêž‰be komo kohuiyamaêž‰ kiyanameheno ebeno kuba ododi komo dito degebolememenaêž‰, kubahaêž‰, mabu amaêž‰ hibilo iyaêž‰tawala, nale dopamo kebe konomo owalubi komo amaêž‰tamo dihatimo, iyo, nale Yaêž‰sukunu komo amaêž‰tamo ba hawakalimi amiaêž‰no kaêž‰kaêž‰ mulaêž‰ gabo baêž‰bo iyaêž‰tumiyaêž‰mata.  
\v 20 Baêž‰bemaêž‰ naeno ekawi, na ubila amaêž‰ baêž‰moe malemale komo Kodawa Kelisoko mabumaêž‰ natamo nododiyaêž‰, baêž‰bene nale ebe ipuwalo ba emedena naeno temeteme komokomo emalagidoleheno gelebadi ukui baêž‰bo kolawemaêž‰nemo.  
\v 21 Baêž‰ hibila, na niyaêž‰tawutamo amaêž‰le naeno tabo komo Onisimasiko mabumaêž‰ dumiminaêž‰ baêž‰bo kopapamiwatamaêž‰naêž‰ta. Iyo, amiaêž‰no malemale natamo konomola, baêž‰bemaêž‰ na iyaêž‰tawala amaêž‰ baêž‰moe kapiya ubi komamo aêž‰kapapamiwatamenaêž‰ta, huiyatiya nale baêž‰moe leta ipuwalo kebe ubi komokomo kahawakalilamitahaêž‰, amaêž‰le baêž‰bi hiliyonomo komamo atumu kakapapamiwatamaêž‰naêž‰ta.   
\p
\v 22 Baêž‰gala eta kapiya komo. Laêž‰ Kolosi sose tawakalubaêž‰te Godoko daêž‰toemehonakoma ebete na du genama guni kuluhukunatenemaêž‰, nale baêž‰be hido komote ebegodone kuluhukumaêž‰ kalakalago latiminamo. Baêž‰be komote duluhukumini nale amaêž‰tamo hibilo kopemaêž‰nemo, baêž‰bemaêž‰ wadiyala amiaêž‰no genamalo haba naêž‰hiduimiyaêž‰ nale amaêž‰go kopemedaêž‰tepamaêž‰.   
\s1 Polote Leta Kuititi Hapulu Tabo Komokomo Dolamagiyaêž‰  
\p
\v 23 Du genamalo nago demedena baêž‰be dubu Epaêž‰palasiti ebeno nolata tabo laêž‰tamo poeme,  
\v 24 baêž‰bene puyaêž‰te baêž‰malo oko nago dowatina, ibi baêž‰ Makako, Aêž‰listakasiko, Dimasiko, baêž‰gala Lukuku, baêž‰moi baêž‰te atumu nolata tabo laêž‰tamo kapoemaêž‰.   
\p
\v 25 Kodawa Yaêž‰su Kelisokono malemale komote laêž‰eno tepo ipuwalo nitanamene. Baêž‰moe baêž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baêž‰baêž‰la.   